==English==
===Etymology===
French, from ''bon'', [[good]], ''appétit'', [[appetite]]

===Interjection phrase===
'''bon appétit!''' (''often'' '''bon appetit!''')

#Used to wish someone enjoyment of the meal they are about to eat.

====Synonyms====
*[[enjoy your meal]]

